	<p class="blue">This system is currently in beta with limited availability. If you would like access, please sign up here.</p>
	
	<p><fb:login-button length="long" onlogin="location.href = '<%= facebook_path %>'" perms="<%= Facebook.config[:perms] %>"></fb:login-button></p>

